  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3372420/extras/22c7f296aeb63b57019e2ecc13b6aeb7.avif?t=1770062540\" width=616 height=90 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Receive, sort, and organize the greatest classics of world literature the way you prefer! From Shakespeare to Flaubert, including Jules Verne and Machado de Assis: in Libritopia, you'll find all the must-have classics for any library!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3372420/extras/a715848659d1798add0bcf3fc827bff8.webp?t=1770062540\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3372420/extras/a715848659d1798add0bcf3fc827bff8.poster.webp?t=1770062540\" class=\"bb_img\" width=800 height=338 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3372420/extras/f1b179f89fb8888169053e0086159441.avif?t=1770062540\" width=616 height=90 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Browse through a variety of colors and palletes to customize your library, choosing your favorite walls, floor, ceiling, windows, curtains and much more! Decorate the space with paintings and plants to build the perfect library for your readers!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3372420/extras/4b6c369742f202d0207e57200d4d1300.webp?t=1770062540\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3372420/extras/4b6c369742f202d0207e57200d4d1300.poster.webp?t=1770062540\" class=\"bb_img\" width=800 height=338 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3372420/extras/ccf12738175588be8a8cdcede622b4b6.avif?t=1770062540\" width=616 height=90 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose your body type, hair, clothes and accessories as you create your own librarian. Express yourself by building different avatars and save them to use at any time. Play with friends to see who will be the \"Librarian of the Month\" an have his/her picture on the office walls!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3372420/extras/5e784a4d57309fc749e4760e6d82f6f5.webp?t=1770062540\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3372420/extras/5e784a4d57309fc749e4760e6d82f6f5.poster.webp?t=1770062540\" class=\"bb_img\" width=800 height=338 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3372420/extras/809d93aeb54c0a040dcf585d3846e5a4.avif?t=1770062540\" width=616 height=90 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Name your library, expand its size, and furnish the space! Set up the environment by placing shelves or using furniture to create corridors. Add labels to each shelf to classify books by genre, author, year, country, even color - or any other way you want! It’s YOUR library.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3372420/extras/40d0e01ad7a2f2c7ec5807855c6663a5.webp?t=1770062540\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3372420/extras/40d0e01ad7a2f2c7ec5807855c6663a5.poster.webp?t=1770062540\" class=\"bb_img\" width=800 height=338 /></picture></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3372420/extras/0ad446d49f1be34795ba4d0d21c7f951.avif?t=1770062540\" width=616 height=90 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Work with friends in multiplayer mode to manage the daily demands of your library. Divide tasks and collaborate to meet all the visitor's needs!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3372420/extras/2946933e49eb46622949d311bab3c1ff.webp?t=1770062540\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3372420/extras/2946933e49eb46622949d311bab3c1ff.poster.webp?t=1770062540\" class=\"bb_img\" width=800 height=338 /></picture></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3372420/extras/7ef9acd7b373634690e685e391ecdbca.avif?t=1770062540\" width=616 height=90 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ensure all visitors can access the books they want! Manage check-outs and book returns, assist visitors with finding books on the shelves, and make sure your library is a peaceful place. No cell phones allowed! Shhhhhh!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3372420/extras/d7bd988dd09c1069056dc6d50345ca9c.webp?t=1770062540\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3372420/extras/d7bd988dd09c1069056dc6d50345ca9c.poster.webp?t=1770062540\" class=\"bb_img\" width=800 height=338 /></picture></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3372420/extras/22c7f296aeb63b57019e2ecc13b6aeb7.avif?t=1770062540\" width=616 height=90 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Receive, sort, and organize the greatest classics of world literature the way you prefer! From Shakespeare to Flaubert, including Jules Verne and Machado de Assis: in Libritopia, you'll find all the must-have classics for any library!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3372420/extras/a715848659d1798add0bcf3fc827bff8.webp?t=1770062540\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3372420/extras/a715848659d1798add0bcf3fc827bff8.poster.webp?t=1770062540\" class=\"bb_img\" width=800 height=338 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3372420/extras/f1b179f89fb8888169053e0086159441.avif?t=1770062540\" width=616 height=90 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Browse through a variety of colors and palletes to customize your library, choosing your favorite walls, floor, ceiling, windows, curtains and much more! Decorate the space with paintings and plants to build the perfect library for your readers!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3372420/extras/4b6c369742f202d0207e57200d4d1300.webp?t=1770062540\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3372420/extras/4b6c369742f202d0207e57200d4d1300.poster.webp?t=1770062540\" class=\"bb_img\" width=800 height=338 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3372420/extras/ccf12738175588be8a8cdcede622b4b6.avif?t=1770062540\" width=616 height=90 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose your body type, hair, clothes and accessories as you create your own librarian. Express yourself by building different avatars and save them to use at any time. Play with friends to see who will be the \"Librarian of the Month\" an have his/her picture on the office walls!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3372420/extras/5e784a4d57309fc749e4760e6d82f6f5.webp?t=1770062540\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3372420/extras/5e784a4d57309fc749e4760e6d82f6f5.poster.webp?t=1770062540\" class=\"bb_img\" width=800 height=338 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3372420/extras/809d93aeb54c0a040dcf585d3846e5a4.avif?t=1770062540\" width=616 height=90 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Name your library, expand its size, and furnish the space! Set up the environment by placing shelves or using furniture to create corridors. Add labels to each shelf to classify books by genre, author, year, country, even color - or any other way you want! It’s YOUR library.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3372420/extras/40d0e01ad7a2f2c7ec5807855c6663a5.webp?t=1770062540\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3372420/extras/40d0e01ad7a2f2c7e